      "writtenOn": "2015-08-19T18:39:40Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "nit: If it is a public member, please document how to use it (when is it initialized for example).\n\nI suggest following the Google3 / Chromium / Android coding convention when declaring structs or classes, i.e.:\n\n1) public methods\n2) public members\n3) private methods\n4) private members\n\nAlso define them in the same order in the corresponding source file.",
